统**\r\n\r\nRaspbian Stretch\r\n\r\n**离线唤醒相关**\r\n\r\n如果是离线唤醒相关的问题，是否已确保 `arecord temp.wav`、`aplay temp.wav` (Linux) 或 `rec temp.wav`、`play temp.wav` （Mac）已正常工作？（注意要求不能带任何其他参数）如果不能，请先配置好麦克风和音响再尝试。\r\n\r\n—— 我已确保录音、播放都正常工作才尝试 wukong-robot 。\r\n\r\n**问题描述**\r\n\r\n使用camera模块的时候，配置了拍照后发送到邮箱，报错\r\n`server_hostname cannot be an empty string or start with a leading dot.`\r\n\r\n**复现步骤**\r\n\r\n拍照成功时，发送邮件会报错\r\n\r\n**已找到解决办法**\r\n在`utils.py`中，使用`smtplib.SMTP()`的时候，要传入`SMTP_SERVER`，即可解决问题，成功发送邮件\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"lmsccc","id":25736473,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI1NzM2NDcz","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/25736473?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc","html_url":"https://github.com/lmsccc","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lmsccc/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/wzpan/wukong-robot/issues/119/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/wzpan/wukong-robot/issues/119/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}